Trichet Says it’s ‘Sometimes Forgotten’ What ECB’s Mandate Is

-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 
2011-10-04T13:16:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/trichet-says-it-s-sometimes-forgotten-what-ecb-s-mandate-is.html
European Central Bank President Jean-
Claude Trichet reiterated that the bank’s primary objective is
maintaining price stability.  “With current discussions sharply focused on how to deal
with the sovereign and fiscal crisis, it is sometimes forgotten
that our mandate is to maintain price stability in the euro
area,” Trichet said in a parliamentary hearing in Brussels
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in Frankfurt at 
